channel.title: PI Dupe Help
channel.description:
Hello i am giving 5m rsgp to someone who helps with this -
Hello rune-server I have a dupe that i cant seem to figure out. ill explain how its done
2 players (a and b)
both players go to fight pits wait for a game to start.
player a kills player b
Then next round player b kills player a.
After that round step out of the waiting room.
tele to duel arena
now either player a or b can stake Make it just one person.
The person who stake MUST WIN!
the loser will respawn back in the fight pits waiting room.
The winner quickly gets to fight pits and gets into the lobby.
The Game starts the LOSER OF THE DUEL MUST KILL THE DUELS WINNER after that leave the waiting room. wahlah the loser got the staked items while the person who staked still has their items...
Any way to fix this? i think it works like this
player a (stakes) wins while server spawns player b into fightpits thinking its still duel arena. Winner comes in game starts loser wins. Server thinking its a rematch. Player leaves lobby with items.

item.description:
@guthix1pker wrote:

i can tell you whats wrong:

someone kills someone else in the duel arena. he won the staked items. then one of the two gets to the fight pits cuz the game thinks its the duel arena.
the orther one gets there too. they fight there and the game thinks oh its fiting at duel arena. then the one that now wins the fight gets the staked items but the orther doesn’t lose em cuz its fight pits and its not dangerous. the answer to the problem: make the game know difference between fight pits and duel arena OR add an special screen for staking OR remove either duel arena or fight pits
